cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CL 

This paper deals with the analysis of visual and textual features from social networks to create personalized fast-forward videos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper also deals with machine learning techniques to infer user preferences, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of text-centric data from social networks also suggests the involvement of information retrieval techniques, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also deals with semantic-aware fast-forward methods, which falls under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the paper also deals with natural language processing techniques to analyze text data, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
